Invite Collaborators:
-Reach out to writers,game developers,narrative designers, and enthusiasts to join and contribute.
Communication Channels:
-Establish channels for communication to foster collaboration and exchange ideas.
Contribution and Review:
-Encourage contributors to share their narrative drafts,story outlines, or ideas through pull requests or designated channels.Review,provide feedback, and iterate collaboratively.
Version Control and Documentation:
-Use Git for version control to track changes and maintain different versions of narratives.Ensure detailed documentation of changes and discussions.
